app_name: Groups Control Groups Messenger Apps Tokee Messenger
app_description: Tokee is a messaging and video calling app. It s fast fun simple and reliable. Tokee strives to connect everyone in the world no matter the distance. Share stories with your friends on your profile and even edit the videos photos you took through the app. Enjoy Tokee anytime and anywhere in real time! PRIVATE MESSAGING Simple secure and reliable messaging Make group chats with all your friends Send fun and cool GIFs to your friends and loved ones Backup your messages media data VOICE VIDEO CALLS Enjoy 1:1 voice and video calls Multi task while on voice video calls PROFILE STORIES Change and customize your Tokee Profile Share daily moments through Status STICKERS A variety of stickers to choose from while chatting Popular stickers and GIFs from GIPHY collection send as many as you like! GIPHY Enjoy the ease of accessing and sending STICKERS EMOJIs and GIFs that GIPHY has to offer Status allows you to share text photos and videos that disappear after 24 hours. Data charges may apply.
